'''阿博'''（{{lang-en|Bo}}<ref name="baseball" />；2008年10月9日－2021年5月8日） 是[[美國|美國]]第44任[[美國總統|總統]][[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]的寵物[[狗|狗]]，也是{{Le|歐巴馬家庭|Family of Barack Obama}}的成員之一。<ref name="fd-two">{{Cite web |last=Dave |first=By |url=http://features.csmonitor.com/politics/2009/04/20/vigilant-press-spots-bo-the-first-dog-out-for-a-walk/ |title=Vigilant press spots Bo, the first dog, out for a walk | csmonitor.com |publisher=Features.csmonitor.com |date=2009-04-20 |accessdate=2009-04-26 |language=en |archive-date=2009-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423055836/http://features.csmonitor.com/politics/2009/04/20/vigilant-press-spots-bo-the-first-dog-out-for-a-walk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="fd-three">{{Cite web |url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/09/04/12/Meet-Bo-the-First-Dog/ |title=The White House - Blog Post - Meet Bo, the First Dog |publisher=Whitehouse.gov |date= |accessdate=2009-08-10 |archive-date=2012-04-24 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67A3twuDp?url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/blog/09/04/12/Meet-Bo-the-First-Dog/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="fd-four">{{Cite news | first = Helen | last = Cooper | title = One Obama Search Ends With a Puppy Named Bo | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/13/us/politics/13obama.html | publisher = The New York Times | date = April 12, 2009 | language = en | accessdate = April 18, 2009 | quote = Other Web sites, which have been tracking the saga of the selection of the first dog, were in a frenzy over the weekend. | archive-date = 2021-05-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210513135232/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/13/us/politics/13obama.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="fd-three" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/127175|title=「阿波」葡萄牙水犬　白宮新成員|accessdate=2018-05-13|date=2009-04-13|publisher=TVBS新聞網|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713073829/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/127175|dead-url=no}}</ref>阿博是一隻[[閹割|已閹割]]<ref name="NBC">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/PETA_Encourages_Obamas_to_Neuter_Neutered_Dog.html|title=PETA Encourages Obamas to Neuter Neutered Dog|last=Hess|first=Amanda|date=2009-04-13|publisher=nbcwashington.com|accessdate=2009-04-15|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205144835/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/PETA_Encourages_Obamas_to_Neuter_Neutered_Dog.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>的雄性黑色長毛[[葡萄牙水犬|葡萄牙水犬]]。<ref name="fd-three" />奧巴馬一家本來沒有養狗，因為他的大女兒瑪麗亞對狗[[過敏|過敏]]。但為了延續白宮主人歷年均有養狗的傳統，第一家庭在入主[[白宮|白宮]]後，花了多個月去觀察各種[[犬種|犬種]]，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/7995570.stm |title=World | Americas | Obama family 'picks first puppy' |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-04-12 |accessdate=2009-04-26 |language=en |archive-date=2017-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818094552/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/7995570.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>並特地選擇了葡萄牙水犬這一種掉毛少的[[低敏狗|低敏狗]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tanews.org.tw/info/3333|title=好命第一狗  歐巴馬親手清狗糞|author=章永安|date=2014-03-25|newspaper=台灣動物新聞網|accessdate=2018-05-13|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012171546/http://www.tanews.org.tw/info/3333|dead-url=no}}</ref>

